ivardefs.name: created
ivardefs.desc: The date when the resource was created.

ivardefs.name: detail_
ivardefs.desc: Distribution of the payment amount for a previously acknowledged payable.

ivardefs.name: disposition
ivardefs.desc: A human readable description of the status of the request for the reconciliation.

ivardefs.name: formCode
ivardefs.desc: A code for the form to be used for printing the content.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: A unique identifier assigned to this payment reconciliation.

ivardefs.name: outcome
ivardefs.desc: The outcome of a request for a reconciliation.

ivardefs.name: paymentAmount
ivardefs.desc: Total payment amount as indicated on the financial instrument.

ivardefs.name: paymentDate
ivardefs.desc: The date of payment as indicated on the financial instrument.

ivardefs.name: paymentIdentifier
ivardefs.desc: Issuer's unique identifier for the payment instrument.

ivardefs.name: paymentIssuer
ivardefs.desc: The party who generated the payment.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period of time for which payments have been gathered into this bulk payment for settlement.

ivardefs.name: processNote_
ivardefs.desc: A note that describes or explains the processing in a human readable form.

ivardefs.name: requestor
ivardefs.desc: The practitioner who is responsible for the services rendered to the patient.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of the resource instance.

properties.desc: This resource provides the details including amount of a payment and allocates the payment items being paid.
